==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Murk
<hw>Murk</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The refuse of fruit, after the juice
has been expressed; marc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Murkily</ent>⟦br⟧
